*Issue*
Currently it's possible to add additional fields to card views in Agile. It would be nice if it were possible to hide the field instead of displaying "None" if there's no value. 
*Workaround for Kanban boards*

Add the following css to the banner:
{noformat}
<style type="text/css">
.ghx-issue .ghx-extra-fields .ghx-fa {
    display: none;
}
</style>
{noformat}

While the 'Workload by Assignee' feature is great, in some circumstances, it has to be disabled.

For example, if there is a company policy which prohibits the display of workload of a single user. Due to this, it would be great to give admins the option to enable/disable this feature.

As a workaround to hide the summary, please add the following JavaScript into the JIRA Announcement Banner:
{code}
<style>
div.ghx-assigned-work-stats
{display:none}
</style>
{code}

