  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *JIRA Software Server*. Using *JIRA Software Cloud*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSWCLOUD-11424].
  {panel}

When viewing Agile board, issue keys on cards are showing at elipses instead of the actual issue key.

This occurs when the first swimlane is collapsed. Uncollapsing the first swimlane will fix the problem.
